<plot>From the people that brought you the cult comedy hit Why We Had To Kill Bitch comes the short film Grim, a witty romantic comedy that turns the "Honey-there's-something-I-need-to-tell-you-about-myself" genre on it's ear. Dan wants to marry Sally. But before he'll let her say "yes" he needs to let her in on a secret about his day job, a secret so unbelievable, so shocking, so Biblical that Sally literally needs to see it to believe it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?223116</url></doc>
